<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(ظ ل ع)</span> : ظَلَعَ الْبَعِيرُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَالرَّجُلُ ظَلْعًا مِنْ بَابِ نَفَعَ غَمَزَ فِي مَشْيِهِ وَهُوَ شَبِيهٌ بِالْعَرَجِ وَلِهَذَا يُقَالُ هُوَ عَرَجٌ يَسِيرٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>